I improved the `Simplify` transformation to remove useless `IfThenElse` nodes. If the condition of a node can be proved true or false, the condition will be removed. For example, TVM often emit duplicated boundary guards like

```cuda
if (threadIdx.y * 100 + threadIdx.x < 1000) {
  if (threadIdx.y * 100 + threadIdx.x < 1000) {
    if (threadIdx.y * 100 + threadIdx.x < 1000) {
      // ...
    }
  }
}
```

This can now be simplified.

